# AGENT CONTEXT: This directory holds all shared libraries in the monorepo.
#
# Each subdirectory here is a pnpm workspace package — a library consumed
# by one or more apps or other packages. Packages are NOT deployed directly;
# they are bundled into apps at build time.
#
# NAMING CONVENTION:
#   packages/ui       → @cmp/ui       (shared React components)
#   packages/utils    → @cmp/utils    (shared utility functions)
#   packages/types    → @cmp/types    (shared TypeScript types/interfaces)
#   packages/config   → @cmp/config   (shared config: eslint, ts, etc.)
#
# STRUCTURE EXPECTATION per package:
#   packages/<name>/
#     package.json    (required — must have "exports" field for tree-shaking)
#     src/
#     tsconfig.json
#     README.md
#
# DEPENDENCY RULE:
#   Packages MAY depend on other packages (but avoid deep chains).
#   Packages MUST NOT depend on apps — this creates circular dependencies.
#
# HOW TO CONSUME A PACKAGE FROM AN APP:
#   In apps/web/package.json:
#     "dependencies": { "@cmp/ui": "workspace:*" }
#   Then: pnpm install (from repo root)
#
# CMP-11 will scaffold the first shared packages.
# This .gitkeep file can be deleted once any real content is committed here.
